---
title: Baked Double Tilapia and Sweet Pepper Orzo with Fresh Veggie Side and Feta
description: These crusted fish fillets are not the only exciting part of this speedy dinner recipe. You'll be blown away by how we use roasted red pepper pesto to flavour both the orzo and fresh veggies.
